Frequently Asked Questions

How to install Jimo?

The setup is lightning-fast. Copy and paste a snippet of JavaScript to your product or integrate via Google Tag Manager. Either way, its super quick! Here is the link to our documentation.

Can I customize my Product Tours?

Yes, customization is a key feature of Jimo. Our powerful editor allows you to design product tours that align perfectly with your product. Design, triggering, or targeting, this flexibility enables you to control the narrative and highlight the features that truly matter.

Can I A/B test different versions of my Product Tours in Jimo?

Of course! Once the A version is fully set up, you can easily duplicate any experience and tweak some parts within the copy to create A/B version. Finally, compare their analytics regularly to see which version performs better.

Are Jimo Product Tours suitable for all types of products?

Yes, Jimo's Tours features are versatile tools that can benefit a wide variety of applications in any industries, crucial for user-oriented product development and improvement.
